{"tid":880301,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"唉屌，想好好地嘆個鋒味漢堡都唔得","createTime":"2018-10-28T15:47:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-28T16:31:03.000Z","uid":81507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"be837b7d3bd16ad108fa047ec4ced940ce520a6c","tid":880301,"uid":81507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T15:47:00.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n<br />\n正話係M記買咗個鋒味漢堡餐，咁小弟我呢排減緊肥，廢事食薯條，所以轉咗個粟米<br />\n<br />\n拎餐個陣由於太期待，再加上趕住返去睇波，所以拎起袋野食就塞撚咗入背囊走人<br />\n<br />\n上到地鐵企企下，feel到背脊至屎忽位濕濕地，心諗今日明明無帶水樽出街，拉開個袋拎個紙袋出黎一睇<br />\n屌你老母個野食紙袋穿撚咗既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲有幾粒粟米係個窿度跌緊出黎<br />\n原來係個粟米杯無合實，連埋d水流出黎搞到個紙袋邊穿咗個窿仔<br />\n<br />\n咁我就諗住唔緊要啦，最緊要睇下個鋒味漢堡有無事<br />\n我伸隻手入去諗住拎個盒包出黎，一拎，成個紙盒拎咗出黎，個鋒味漢堡就仲係個袋入面，呢個時候我已經好撚尷尬，但都心諗好彩仲有個紙袋裝住<br />\n<br />\n點知摸一摸袋底，仆街濕撚晒，俾我摸多兩摸仲要穿撚埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我即刻將所有野俾晒右手攞，留返隻左手淨係托住個紙袋同入面個鋒味漢堡，d汁係咁滴落我隻手，我唯有用掌心兜撚住d汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後真係無辦法，係下站落咗車，出閘個陣因爲要拎八達通，所以要搵個無乜人既地方fing走d汁先騰到隻手出黎出閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要企係垃圾桶隔離三兩啖啃鳩咗個飽佢<br />\n<br />\n明明平時都係買完即刻放入背囊入面都無事，點解就係今次咁on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2c99dac986fe00f33cbd62d00c124ca145e6860","tid":880301,"uid":68883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T15:48:21.000Z","msg":"有是咁的<br />\n<br />\n1/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7164e2d4cc4922c797f9ecc7607b99ce5394a94b","tid":880301,"uid":81507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2c99dac986fe00f33cbd62d00c124ca145e6860","tid":880301,"uid":68883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T15:48:21.000Z","msg":"有是咁的<br />\n<br />\n1/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T15:51:26.000Z","msg":"講大話爛春袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2337083ae1df5748336292b990b9b0fd42c21edb","tid":880301,"uid":218610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T16:05:21.000Z","msg":"屌你老味個乜撚野鋒味漢堡搞到我柯撚左兩晚呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f575b5850c47ba0c552c831fcc314aa32db940ba","tid":880301,"uid":81507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2337083ae1df5748336292b990b9b0fd42c21edb","tid":880301,"uid":218610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T16:05:21.000Z","msg":"屌你老味個乜撚野鋒味漢堡搞到我柯撚左兩晚呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T16:31:03.000Z","msg":"你個飽唔乾淨掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}